scenes.description: Cecilia stands on a fiery clockwork stage, discussing the intense heat and her mascot Otomo's newfound 'hatred'.
The stage transitions to a serene green forest theme. Cecilia introduces her team 'Justice' and prepares for her performance.
Cecilia performs a 3D cover of 'Baragoku Otome'.
